<Sect1 Id="ToDrawARectangleTA">
<Title>To Draw a Rectangle</Title>
<IndexTerm>
<Primary>rectangle:drawing</Primary>
</IndexTerm>
<OrderedList>
<ListItem Id="HICND.TSKS.item.53">
<Para>Select the Rectangle tool from the palette.
</Para>
<Graphic Entityref="IconEditorRectangleTool" Id="HICND.TSKS.fig.3"></Graphic>
</ListItem>
<ListItem Id="HICND.TSKS.item.54">
<Para>Click in the drawing area and drag to stretch the outline of the
rectangle.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem Id="HICND.TSKS.item.55">
