<Sect1 Id="ToUndoADrawingOperationTA">
<Title>To Undo a Drawing Operation</Title>
<ItemizedList Mark="&bull;">
<ListItem Id="HICND.TSKS.item.96">
<Para>Choose Undo from the Edit menu.
</Para>
</ListItem>
</ItemizedList>
<Para>Only the most recent change can be undone.</Para>
</Sect1>
<Sect1 Id="ToOpenAnExistingIconTA">
<Title>To Open an Existing Icon</Title>
<OrderedList>
<ListItem Id="HICND.TSKS.item.97">
<Para>Choose Open from the File menu.</Para>
<Para>If you have unsaved changes, Icon Editor warns you that your changes
will be lost by loading another icon. Click Cancel to cancel the Open
command. Click OK if you don't want to save your changes.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem Id="HICND.TSKS.item.98">
<Para>Type the name of the icon file you want to load or select it from the
list.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem Id="HICND.TSKS.item.99">
<Para>Click Open.</Para>
</ListItem>
</OrderedList>
<Note>
<Para>When you load a file, the output format is automatically set to the
format of the file you load.
</Para>
</Note>
<Procedure>
