<ListItem Id="HICND.TSKS.item.119">
<Para>Select the Selection tool (bottom right of the tool palette).</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem Id="HICND.TSKS.item.120">
<Para>Press mouse button 1 and drag a box around the area you want to select.</Para>
<Para>A box flashes around the selected area.</Para>
</ListItem>
</OrderedList>
<Procedure>
